# Super Reviewer generated capture output (LLM judge artifacts, not source)
# CaptureOutput/ = volatile JSON/MD per run — not committed
Tests/SuperReviewer/CaptureOutput/*
!Tests/SuperReviewer/CaptureOutput/.gitkeep
# RegressionLocks/ = committed — these are the frozen regression fixtures
# (no ignore rule needed; locks are intentionally versioned)
